text: Prithvirajsing Roopun GCSK (born 24 May 1959), also known as Pradeep Singh Roopun, is a Mauritian politician. He has been the President of Mauritius since 2019. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Mauritius Category:Current national leaders
title: Prithvirajsing Roopun
